WEBVTT

00:01:57.234 --> 00:02:01.097
hoping to dilute the infection
surging through his blood.

00:02:01.497 --> 00:02:04.603
Nothing worked. He died.

00:02:05.143 --> 00:02:07.705
He was 30 years old.

00:02:08.115 --> 00:02:10.088
If you look back through history,

00:02:10.088 --> 00:02:13.362
most people died the way
my great uncle died.

00:02:13.362 --> 00:02:16.032
Most people didn't die
of cancer or heart disease,

00:02:16.032 --> 00:02:20.120
the lifestyle diseases that afflict us
in the West today.

00:02:20.490 --> 00:02:24.229
They didn't die of those diseases
because they didn't live long enough

00:02:24.229 --> 00:02:26.225
to develop them.

00:02:26.225 --> 00:02:28.338
They died of injuries --

00:02:28.338 --> 00:02:30.823
being gored by an ox,